item.title: Help me remove this? PI Base - NOTHING WORKS!
item.dc:creator: @belhelmiel belhelmiel
item.description:
@belhelmiel wrote:

[quote=“rang3 pkz, post:9, topic:402173”]I’m trying to make a Cammy PvP. I need the doors gone. Voetbal, that won’t work either.

PAYING TO REMOVE THESE GATES! Will pay RSGP![/quote]
Your not suppose to offer money just rep++. What you could do is add a fire under the gate when you wanna get in or look around for a different object that is possible to delete. Or if you want to modify it I think theres something for that you can rotate it and stuff. I don’t think that would work though I tried it. The best way is to go in action handler and make it teleport you to the inside of the gate when you click on one side. And the other side teleport you back out of the closed in area. So you can get in and out. I had to do that for my gate at home. But I didn’t have to make an out teleport they both take you into the closed area because theres another way out. The gates there for quicker access. Or you could just fix the gates to where they open. But I dont know how to do that. There is probably tutorials all over for that.
